Tunde Opalana, Abuja The National Working Committee (NWC) of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has approved the nomination of a five-member Screening Committee to screen all aspirants for the North-West Zonal Executive Committee positions. National Organizing Secretary, Col Austin Akobundu (rtd) in a statement Wednesday listed; Alh. Shehu Baba Agaie (Chairman), Sen. Grace Bent (Member), Hon. Nura Amadi (Member), Dr. Danladi Abdul-Hameed (Member) and Alh. Baba Iyali (Secretary) The Screening exercise is scheduled to hold today, Thursday April 8, 2021 at the Zonal Headquarters, i.e. Kaduna City, Kaduna State.